snippet.title: NBA 2K19: Broadcast Trailer
snippet.description: Basketball guru Bill Simmons joins NBA legends Kobe Bryant and Kevin Garnett in this year's broadcast booth. Get an early listen to some of the sounds of NBA 2K19.
